{"tid":1509150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(賣港狗)班建制狗同泛民原來去左美國想阻止國會成立人權及民主法案!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-08-26T17:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T18:29:05.000Z","uid":131157,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0a1e5be0bdb984e96623acc1f68dc25a1b52bd86","tid":1509150,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:39:57.000Z","msg":"同販民班仆街割蓆<br />\n現在是美國國會成立香港人權及民主法的關鍵時刻。只要美國成立此法，香港進入英美共管時代，香港人成功奪回香港及保護義士，得到普選。<br />\n販民四人幫竟然聯同建制派到美國見美國議員阻止美國國會成立香港人權及民主法。要是他們成功，香港會進入黑暗時代，義士會被囚禁及毒打，強姦凌辱，香港永不超生。<br />\n香港人給販民很多選票和捐款，數十年來被販民欺騙，誤了香港前途。現在是時候跟販民分化割蓆。<br />\n我們要組織力量圍販民辦事處，向販民議員喝倒采。這樣才能令美國國會議員知道，販民議員不代表香港人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3046311008744058&amp;id=189060481135806\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D3046311008744058%26id%3D189060481135806&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQroVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=f15b7d82\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3046311008744058&amp;id=189060481135806</a>"},{"pid":"4538cf84967249ebfbb1d1148414bdf7eb4e2752","tid":1509150,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:40:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQroVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=256f3a4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQroVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=4c6f6fe7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />